msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard"

msgid "Logout"
msgstr "Abmelden"

msgid "Login"
msgstr "Anmelden"

msgid "Get Started"
msgstr "Loslegen"

msgid "Contact"
msgstr "Kontakt"

msgid "Learn smarter, not harder."
msgstr "Lerne smarter, nicht harter."

msgid "The smarter way to study"
msgstr "Der smarteste Weg zu lernen"

msgid "Master any subject"
msgstr "Beherrsche jedes Fach"

msgid "at your own pace"
msgstr "in deinem eigenen Tempo"

msgid "Create custom word lists with flexible study fields. Study with flashcards,"
msgstr "Erstelle eigene Wortlisten mit flexiblen Lernfeldern. Lerne mit Karteikarten,"

msgid "track your progress, and actually remember what you learn."
msgstr "verfolge deinen Fortschritt und behalte wirklich, was du lernst."

msgid "Start for free"
msgstr "Kostenlos starten"

msgid "Definition"
msgstr "Definition"

msgid "Lasting for a very short time"
msgstr "Nur sehr kurz andauernd"

msgid "The ephemeral beauty of cherry blossoms"
msgstr "Die fluchtige Schonheit der Kirschbluten"

msgid "Everything you need to study effectively"
msgstr "Alles, was du fur effektives Lernen brauchst"

msgid "Custom Study Lists"
msgstr "Individuelle Lernlisten"

msgid "Create word lists tailored to any subject — vocabulary, formulas, dates, concepts."
msgstr "Erstelle Wortlisten fur jedes Fach — Vokabeln, Formeln, Daten, Konzepte."

msgid "Flexible Fields"
msgstr "Flexible Felder"

msgid "Add as many fields as you need per word: description, examples, notes, and more."
msgstr "Fuge pro Wort so viele Felder hinzu, wie du brauchst: Beschreibung, Beispiele, Notizen und mehr."

msgid "Fast & Simple"
msgstr "Schnell und einfach"

msgid "A clean interface that gets out of your way so you can focus on learning."
msgstr "Eine klare Oberflache, damit du dich auf das Lernen konzentrieren kannst."

msgid "Have a question or feedback? We would love to hear from you."
msgstr "Frage oder Feedback? Wir freuen uns auf deine Nachricht."

msgid "We usually reply within 24 hours."
msgstr "Wir antworten in der Regel innerhalb von 24 Stunden."

msgid "Back to home"
msgstr "Zuruck zur Startseite"

msgid "Sign in"
msgstr "Anmelden"

msgid "Please log in to continue."
msgstr "Bitte melde dich an, um fortzufahren."

msgid "Quiz Complete!"
msgstr "Quiz abgeschlossen!"

msgid "Your score"
msgstr "Dein Ergebnis"

msgid "Excellent work!"
msgstr "Ausgezeichnete Arbeit!"

msgid "Good job!"
msgstr "Gute Arbeit!"

msgid "Keep practicing!"
msgstr "Weiter uben!"

msgid "Try Again"
msgstr "Erneut versuchen"

msgid "Back to Dashboard"
msgstr "Zuruck zum Dashboard"
